          <title>MLB Tests Robot Umpires, Sees 2026 Big League Use Possible</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Major League Baseball is set to test robot umpires as part of a challenge system during spring training at 13 ballparks hosting 19 teams. The experiment could lead to regular-season use in 2026.]]></description>
